# name: TAK TEX 08 - Producent no products
# description: Po procesie żaden konsument nie ma produktu.
# source: checkpoint2_v1.tex, sekcja Producent i konsumenci
# expected: TAK

fluents empty, hasA, hasB
actions put, getA, getB, consumeA, consumeB
initially !empty and hasA and hasB
put causes !empty if true
getA causes empty and hasA if !empty
getB causes empty and hasB if !empty
consumeA causes !hasA if hasA
consumeB causes !hasB if hasB
